event.title: CEO of Hell's Bay Boatworks Presents
event.info: The eClub proudly presents Chris Peterson, founder of Hell's Bay Boatworks. Today Hell's Bay Boatworks is still led by a team of dedicated fishermen, outdoorsmen and adventurers. This team is guided by Capt. Chris Peterson and his wife Wendi Peterson. Chris not only brings years of on the water experience, but has a depth of business experience leading companies and large organizations for more than 20 years. All of the department leads at Hell's Bay have been with the Boatworks more than five years and have a proven dedication to creating the finest skiffs available. Everyone at Hell's Bay is passionate about what they create and their passion shows in the Hell's Bay's finished skiffs.
